    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> PZO9210</p>\r\n<p>This alchemical concoction can be spread over a Medium or Small creature's body as a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Full-Round-Actions\">full-round action</a>. It provides a +5 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Bonus-Alchemical-\">alchemical bonus</a> on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/escape-artist\">Escape Artist</a> checks, CMD checks to avoid a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Grapple\">grapple</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\">Reflex</a> saves to avoid an ooze's improved grab or engulf abilities, but gives a -5 penalty to <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Disarm\">disarm</a> checks, <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Grapple\">grapple</a> checks to start or maintain a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Grapple\">grapple</a> or <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Pinned\">pin</a>, and other checks that may be hindered by a loose grip (such as <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/climb\">Climb</a>). One application lasts for up to 1 hour and can be removed with soap and water.</p>\r\n<p><b>Create</b>: <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/craft\">Craft</a> (alchemy) DC 25</p>\r\n",
